    "NameAccuracyNameAccuracyAlpaca (chavinlo)33.6%LLaMA 7B32.7%Alpaca (wxjiao)46.4%MPT-7B-Instruct40.9%BloomZ 7B37.3%OpenLLaMA 7B Instruct31.8%Dolly v1 6B31.8%OpenLLaMA 7B OpenInst.30.0%Falcon 7B Instruct40.0%OPT 6.7b18.2%GPT-J 6b18.2%StableLM 7B11.8%GPT-JT 6B28.2%WizardLM 7B47.3%Instruct GPT-J 6B39.1%Wombat 7B44.5%Wombat 7B GPT440.9%initial tests, BloomZ was the best model in the 7B parameter range with 35.5% accuracy.",
